comments: Nurkic (POR) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Brooks (MEM) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) briefly places his hand to Morant's (MEM) front and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) veers slightly in Melton's (MEM) path with a bent arm to his side and marginal contact occurs as he releases during his drive.
Melton (MEM) makes marginal contact to McCollum's (POR) arm after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) clamps and holds Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm, affecting his ability to get to the rebound.  Jackson Jr. then grabs and pulls Nurkic's jersey.
Covington (POR) makes contact with Morant's (MEM) arm and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) arm during his drive and he is able to move through the contact.
Tillman (MEM) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) hand after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Melton (MEM) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Brooks (MEM) jumps along Powell's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Powell (POR) places his arm to Morant's (MEM) front moving alongside of him and marginal contact occurs during his drive.
Brooks (MEM) places his arm to Lillard's (POR) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Covington (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in Brooks' (MEM) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Melton (MEM) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it from Nurkic (POR) during his shot attempt at the basket.
Tillman (MEM) briefly engages with Nurkic (POR) in the post during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Tillman (MEM) places a resting hand to Nurkic's (POR) backside and does not apply force defending his shot attempt at the basket.
Nurkic (POR) commits a take foul on Melton (MEM).
MEM is whistled a Delay of Game Violation.
Anderson (MEM) initiates contact to Lillard's (POR) body and contact affects his SQBR.  The contact occurs before Lillard is in his shooting motion.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Jackson Jr. (MEM).
